snippet.title: Konkan Coast Pirate Solutions - Trailer
snippet.description:
Konkan Coast Pirate Solutions is a puzzle game about helping pirate ships do pirate things. 

Set up the simulations. Watch how the ships behave. Explore how the systems interact.

Releasing on 1st March 2023.
 
Wishlist on Steam Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2156410/Konkan_Coast_Pirate_Solutions/
